{"tid":2495902,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"你地睇完漫畫仲會唔會睇動畫？？？","createTime":"2021-04-19T12:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T13:40:59.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f32c080e41c41b0559ddfdc33377ab9b1fda937","tid":2495902,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"睇完漫畫都知道晒d 劇情發展，<br />\n再睇返動畫會唔會覺得悶 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 巨人未睇結局，本身睇緊動畫，諗緊睇唔睇漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擔心俾漫畫劇透完再睇動畫，會唔會冇咁爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b4292bd649b6d61b6ab6c73236e6faa0c92987","tid":2495902,"uid":5137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"a32059695d75e267dd83545405e77b12ec72c8f4","tid":2495902,"uid":370738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"real"},{"pid":"4424812cde71973cba457ae87ddbba7f5b99ed3a","tid":2495902,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"心情好抖結 ...  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06651984480ab91c59699f7afe8ca2a850155444","tid":2495902,"uid":349439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:49:48.000Z","msg":"漫畫睇原畫，畫風，故事<br />\n動畫睇色彩，分鏡同聽聲優演繹<br />\n2種唔同嘅體驗嚟㗎，鍾意個作品一定會睇哂<br />\n同埋有時動畫會刪劇情或者改到啲次序亂哂"},{"pid":"2c4d75f2361a0cd064fd2b39e94dc8c936caf27c","tid":2495902,"uid":215763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先唔係間間動畫製作公司都係ufo、骨頭同mappa<br />\n同埋唔知係咪睇慣漫畫，成日形住動畫個上色風格唔靚"},{"pid":"a86754e489cffc1a84e3e0202444fbbc40909bd1","tid":2495902,"uid":273726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"本身同你一樣處境<br />\n為左可以同朋友討論&amp;比人陰啲陰啲劇透<br />\n最後睇左漫畫<br />\n最緊要都係知道故事劇情<br />\n之後會唔會睇動畫都係其次 無話哂唔哂<br />\n一炮過睇完好爽<br />\n<br />\n睇完有強烈空虛感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再思考返整個故事又回味無窮<br />\n<br />\n無後悔睇漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0abcb459ccbefcfcfd7d4468f2af54454fd6c66","tid":2495902,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n動畫同漫畫既演繹方式都唔同<br />\n配樂 聲優 氣氛 呢啲黑白既漫畫都做唔到"},{"pid":"66687c2a36a067896c4e36f874b643dcb8a5efd9","tid":2495902,"uid":279315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"真係唔會睇,畫風爭好遠對比起動畫"},{"pid":"be7a18d858361ba399ee7a273cadc1d7b8c1e4ac","tid":2495902,"uid":311835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"會 除非動畫好垃圾/漫畫爛尾"}]}